The ANC in Kwazulu-Natal is gearing up for its elective conference this weekend after a series of postponements. Courtesy #dstv403    DURBAN - The ANC in KwaZulu-Natal is gearing up for its elective conference this weekend after a series of postponements. It's back-to-back meetings between the party's steering committee and the KZN Provincial Executive Committee. eNCA senior reporter Siphamandla Goge shares more details in the video above.